imdb.plot outline: In 2007, at 7 years old, Reese began hosting Piper's Picks TV in Wellington, Florida and became the youngest video podcaster on the Internet. Each episode features Reese's take on a chosen topic, such as food, theme park rides, films, and television shows, or more recently, the episodes have featured interviews with celebrities
imdb.title: Piper's Picks TV
plot: In 2007, at 7 years old, Reese began hosting _Piper's Picks TV_ (qv) in Wellington, Florida and became the youngest video podcaster on the Internet. Each episode features Reese's take on a chosen topic, such as food, theme park rides, films, and television shows, or more recently, the episodes have featured interviews with celebrities::Rebekah Willows
